# This is example Modules

To give information for how to develop in module way using Vue Js.

- Copy the Resources/assets folder to your newly created module directory.

- cd into Modules/YOUR_MODULES

- Go To app.js, change the el name

        const app = new Vue({
            el: '#app-example',
            store,
            router
        });

- Go To router.js, change Base:

        const router = new VueRouter({
            base: '/example',
            mode: 'history',
            routes
        })

- Go To index.blade.php, change the id name, link and srcipt reference :

        <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ mix('css/example.css') }}">
        <div id="app-example">
            <router-view></router-view>
        </div>
        <script src="{{ mix('js/example.js') }}"></script>

run

        npm install
        npm run dev
